localhost/slim3-application

Required
===============
composer - https://getcomposer.org/
slim - https://github.com/slimphp/Slim
twig - https://github.com/slimphp/Twig-View
bootstrap
jquery
Eloquent (from Laravel)
database with test data
respect validation
slim csrf - https://github.com/slimphp/Slim-Csrf
slim flash - https://github.com/slimphp/Slim-Flash

===============

install composer
download source: https://getcomposer.org/

on your cmd type the command below to check if composer is installed
>composer

-----------------------------
our project folder is:- slim3-application

-----------------------------
so create and navigate to your project folder
>cd C:\xampp\htdocs\slim3-application


install slim 3
>composer require slim/slim "^3.0"


install twig
>composer require slim/twig-view

add psr-4 in the composer.json file and run the following command
>composer dump-autoload -o

install Eloquent
>composer require illuminate/database


install respect validation
>composer require respect/validation


install slim csrf
>composer require slim/csrf


install slim flash for showing flash messages
>composer require slim/flash


create the public directory and add the index.php file
create the bootstrap directory and add the app.php file
create the app directory and add the routes.php file

create the .htaccess file - turn url rewriting on

clousers
------------
$app->get('/',function($request, $response){
    return "ok";
});

aoutoload - PSR-4
